LEGENDARY Nigerian musician, Evangelist Ebenezer Obey will join Nathaniel Bassey and other gospel acts for Funke Felix-Adejumo’s Winning Edge 2022. Obey, according to Felix-Adejumo, will be ministering in songs to a large gathering of women today, Saturday, July 15, 2022.   Premier Music appoints Michael Odiong as new General Manager     My parents aren’t forcing me to do music, Burna Boy’s sister…     Lagos state announces plans to immortalise Sound Sultan   The event will also have in attendance Jerry Eze, Jumoke Adenowo, Bishop Felix Adejumo, Sola Adesakin, Dunsin Oyekan, Beejay Sax, Tim Godfrey, Tope Alabi, Sammie Okposo, and Sinach. The annual international conference for women is organised to validate womanhood, discuss and resolve women issues like career, politics, marriage, singleness, abuse, divorce, leadership, widowhood, violence, and parenting among others. Speaking on the forthcoming event, the convener, Felix-Adejumo, said, this year’s event, which will be held at the Tafawa Balewa Square, Onikan, Lagos, will be celebrating and empowering women for greatness.